Hi, kiddo. Where's Dad?

194
00:32:59,947 --> 00:33:01,779
Let me catch my breath.

195
00:33:01,949 --> 00:33:03,850
I hope you brought trout.

196
00:33:03,985 --> 00:33:05,510
