What were you talking about?

228
00:34:36,577 --> 00:34:38,910
We were riding each other,
that's all.

229
00:34:40,147 --> 00:34:41,945
Not me, mostly Marco.

230
00:34:42,083 --> 00:34:43,949
Marco and Sam fought?

231
00:34:44,151 --> 00:34:47,952
